      (2018), https://www.isi.fraunhofer.de/content/dam/isi/dokumente/ccx/2018/Technical%20and%20economic%20feasability.pdf<br/>Un-levelized
      capital cost of heating - Metric: Un-levelized capital cost of heating - Cost
      type: capex - Energy carrier: bioenergy - Heating type: local_heating - Assumption'
